Note that LR-like parsing algorithms were proposed by Schabes and Vijay-Shanker (1990) and Nederhof (1998). 
The complete construction of LR-style parser for TAGs can be found in Schabes and Vijay-Shanker (1990). 
2The algorithm described here can be extended to use SLR(1) tables (Schabes and Vijay-Shanker, 1990). 
